  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released\u00a003/07/2017 at 10:47 CT (16:47 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.11.1-TicketFormSignatures\">Ticket Form Signatures</h2><p>Signature previews would not always display properly\u00a0for unsaved forms, although they would be saved and presented properly after save. To prevent any confusion, we made a few adjustments to how signatures are previewed for saved\u00a0forms.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.11.1-AnalyticsIndex\">Analytics Index</h2><p>The analytics index page received some updates to reflect the new language describing the Business Intelligence Suite features.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.11.1-InventoryLabelImages\">Inventory Label Images</h2><p>The maximum image size is now constrained to 3 inches wide.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.11.1-SupplierOverrides\">Supplier Overrides</h2><p>For\u00a0items backordered on a ticket and ordered through a PO, the\u00a0supplier record could get cleared out when re-saving the ticket. This issue has been resolved.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.11.1-InventoryExpenseReport\">Inventory Expense Report</h2><p>The shipping cost was not adjusting based on the inventory date filters set on the Inventory Expense Report.\u00a0The shipping cost will now obey the filters appropriately.</p>",
